name: I'm New Here
description:
Interactive 3D Object with Something
(yea, I know it's the same ol' digital collage, well at least I tried).

Another continuation of my collage making exploration, trying something new. We'll see where this thing going to take me.

Title taken from Gil Scott-Heron's song
"I did not become someone different
That I did not want to be
But I'm new here
Will you show me around"
